It may also belong to the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category as it involves encoding and decoding of information. The use of tensor factorization suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The use of numerical methods and optimization techniques suggests that it may belong to the mathematical modeling (cs.MM) and numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories.
